{
  "lesson": "WC-PB-14",
  "audioMaster": "training/playbooks/WC-PB-14-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 210.834,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Someone says a page is broken.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.865,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Before you believe them, or doubt them, reproduce it.",
      "startS": 2.113,
      "endS": 4.324,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Load the exact address they used, then read two things:",
      "startS": 4.572,
      "endS": 5.517,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "the URL in the bar, and the message on the screen.",
      "startS": 5.79,
      "endS": 9.287,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Three very different failures hide behind that one complaint,",
      "startS": 9.507,
      "endS": 12.341,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "and those two reads are what tell them apart.",
      "startS": 12.601,
      "endS": 18.64,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Class one is the hard four-oh-four.",
      "startS": 19.113,
      "endS": 21.42,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "The Settings hub lists Logic P-O-S links,",
      "startS": 22.083,
      "endS": 24.824,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "and when they were last confirmed in July they served the web server's own error page.",
      "startS": 25.15,
      "endS": 27.025,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "No Wash Central header. No sidebar.",
      "startS": 27.334,
      "endS": 29.742,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Just the server saying it has no file at that address.",
      "startS": 30.379,
      "endS": 32.826,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Their status today is parked, so re-check on your own tenant before quoting it.",
      "startS": 33.265,
      "endS": 41.459,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "The same class wears a second face inside the app.",
      "startS": 41.92,
      "endS": 46.662,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "System Alerts still sits in the IT and Support menu,",
      "startS": 46.662,
      "endS": 50.194,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "yet on July ninth the page answered with an HTTP four-oh-four.",
      "startS": 50.194,
      "endS": 54.464,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "So a listed feature can still four-oh-four.",
      "startS": 54.464,
      "endS": 56.936,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "That usually means release gated, or mid deploy.",
      "startS": 56.936,
      "endS": 60.172,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Never tell a client the feature doesn't exist.",
      "startS": 60.172,
      "endS": 63.405,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "Class two looks like nothing at all.",
      "startS": 63.84,
      "endS": 65.979,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Fundraiser sits in the C-R-M sidebar like any other entry.",
      "startS": 66.475,
      "endS": 70.034,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Click it, and watch the address bar.",
      "startS": 70.418,
      "endS": 72.257,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "The URL just gains a trailing hash mark, and the page never changes.",
      "startS": 72.752,
      "endS": 76.95,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "That is a stub. A menu item with no page wired behind it.",
      "startS": 77.253,
      "endS": 81.308,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Not a four-oh-four, and not their connection.",
      "startS": 81.653,
      "endS": 84.239,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Class three fools the most people.",
      "startS": 84.736,
      "endS": 88.05,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Open Terminals, under Hardware.",
      "startS": 88.05,
      "endS": 90.361,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "The page loads.",
      "startS": 90.361,
      "endS": 91.571,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "Breadcrumb, KPI, buttons, column headers, all there.",
      "startS": 91.571,
      "endS": 94.394,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "But where the rows belong, it says it couldn't load records.",
      "startS": 94.394,
      "endS": 99.228,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Failed to fetch.",
      "startS": 99.228,
      "endS": 100.72,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Now look at what did render.",
      "startS": 101.12,
      "endS": 102.788,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Header, sidebar, KPIs, columns. Only the data is missing.",
      "startS": 103.713,
      "endS": 106.834,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "The page shell arrived fine and one background call failed,",
      "startS": 107.218,
      "endS": 108.53,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "and that is usually transient.",
      "startS": 108.969,
      "endS": 112.094,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "On July ninth this same banner hit roughly sixty pages at once.",
      "startS": 112.459,
      "endS": 114.147,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "That's one service hiccup, not sixty broken screens.",
      "startS": 115,
      "endS": 122.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Put the three side by side.",
      "startS": 122.789,
      "endS": 124.188,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Whole page replaced by an error, at the address you asked for: hard four-oh-four.",
      "startS": 124.805,
      "endS": 128.05,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "A click that does nothing but add a hash mark: dead stub.",
      "startS": 128.35,
      "endS": 129.679,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "A page frame with a failed-records panel inside it: data-fetch error.",
      "startS": 130.472,
      "endS": 133.776,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "One look at the screen, plus the URL, settles it.",
      "startS": 134.596,
      "endS": 142.08,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "Whichever class it is, capture the same evidence.",
      "startS": 142.48,
      "endS": 145.574,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "The exact URL. A screenshot of the message.",
      "startS": 145.975,
      "endS": 147.314,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "The module you were in, where you clicked from, and what you expected to load.",
      "startS": 147.697,
      "endS": 149.105,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Then the class-specific note: for a four-oh-four, whether it's a known parked item.",
      "startS": 149.529,
      "endS": 153.912,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "For a stub, say so. For a fetch error, whether a refresh clears it.",
      "startS": 154.375,
      "endS": 164.48,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Then escalate from Support Tickets, under IT and Support.",
      "startS": 164.88,
      "endS": 168.661,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "On a real issue, on your tenant, the new ticket carries all five facts plus the class.",
      "startS": 169.544,
      "endS": 175.158,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "Two exceptions.",
      "startS": 175.834,
      "endS": 176.689,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "A fetch error that clears on refresh needs no ticket at all,",
      "startS": 177.185,
      "endS": 180.524,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "and migration switches go to Jira, not here.",
      "startS": 180.929,
      "endS": 183.508,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "On the shared demo, nothing gets submitted.",
      "startS": 184.12,
      "endS": 186.397,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "That's the sort.",
      "startS": 186.8,
      "endS": 187.612,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "Read the URL, read the message, pick the class.",
      "startS": 188.397,
      "endS": 191.849,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "Hard four-oh-four? Escalate it as a serving problem.",
      "startS": 192.347,
      "endS": 193.322,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Dead stub? Log it as release gated, never as gone.",
      "startS": 193.795,
      "endS": 195.718,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Fetch error? Refresh first, and escalate only if it sticks.",
      "startS": 196.125,
      "endS": 196.91,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "Three problems that look identical from a distance, told apart in one glance.",
      "startS": 197.441,
      "endS": 210.387,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}